title: [Glaoveln, V'Koort Docks]
description: The dockyard is shrouded in an eerie mist that blankets the entire area, adding to the deep chill that settles in from the arctic shores beyond.  The wooden piers creak and groan as krolvin ships sway gently in the murky waters.  The salty air is thick with the smell of fish and seaweed.
